title: Number of live births in the EU in 2018
yAxis: Number of live births in millions
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of live births in millions, containing a total of 11 data points.
Overall Number of live births in millions has decreased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Number of live births in millions, about 5.47 was reported at Year 2008
Minimum Number of live births in millions about 4.96 was reached at Year 2018
